a:50:{i:1124987;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124987";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:105:"/me smacks brain for only being able to think of Frozen when uncontrollable emotion-based magic comes up.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417234845";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172349200";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1124988;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124988";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:251:"Well, magic in the show seems to match the users tempo and mood, like how casting most spells requires the caster to be calm. I work under the assumption magic becomes erratic when angry and such. So, having a field of it behaves in a similar fashion.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417234848";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172348376";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1124989;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124989";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:10:"Let it go~";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417234868";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172348579";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1124990;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124990";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:63:"/me smacks Dark for only making Frozen more prevalent in brain!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417234904";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172349788";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1124993;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124993";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:157:"/me thinks smacking is a silly idea. I do like starting from scratch though, means I can make Dark more easy to rp with, make him actually sorta like ponies.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417234962";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172349529";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1124994;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124994";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:467:"See, I honestly think the biggest criteria for whether or not magical things should be approved is how well thought-out they are. The only really bad ones that step too far outside the canon boundaries are the ones that don&#039;t have limits established by the player ahead of time. Most of the other ones, in my experience, are actually pretty good and make for excellent roleplay. They don&#039;t even seem non-canon when they&#039;re handled by experienced rpers.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417234994";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172350689";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1124996;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124996";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:3:" :D";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235044";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172350341";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1124998;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124998";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:154:"I might re-construct Dark&#039;s old story (With less murder), throw it some place else and talk to Ayame, Saph&#039;s is cool. Unlike a particular two...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235098";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172350885";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1124999;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1124999";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:348:"Also in my experience has been that people will have these semi-ridiculous, totally-not-canon ideas for magic stuff, and then they&#039;ll suddenly become canon with the new season/episode. Like the show creators read their mind or something, and then the roleplay moderaders are just like &#039;what the frick frack diddlydack just happened?&#039;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235118";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172351924";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125000;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125000";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:141:"SapphireNight is one of the coolest characters I&#039;ve ever come across. I still wonder how she swung that one to get the Mayday thumbs-up.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235152";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172352267";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125001;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125001";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:10:"Iona, too.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235166";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172352413";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125002;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125002";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:25:"Ohh that was a fun one...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235173";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172351636";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125003;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125003";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:33:"Iona&#039;s was biased I believe.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235188";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172351788";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125005;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125005";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:132:"I&#039;m like 99% sure that one was totally biased. The character was created long before changelings existed in the pony universe. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235224";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172352986";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125006;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125006";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:59:"Also I think that was coincidence meeting with opportunity.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235292";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172352819";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125009;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125009";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:306:"Confession Time: I actually had another account on Fillydelphia a few years back where I just intentionally tried to annoy Mayday with these outrageous characters. Most of them got deleted, but there are still remnants (http://fillydelphia.com/chat/player.php?name=1265). There were some fun ones in there.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235447";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172355214";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125015;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125015";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:23:"hahahahahaha Brilliant ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235691";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172356814";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125016;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125016";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:296:"It &lt;i&gt;was&lt;/i&gt; brilliant... until I actually cursed at her about something and she banned my IP from the website for a month or so. I eventually pleaded mercy via email so she&#039;d let me back on, and then I created a new account and started over with &#039;serious&#039; characters.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235770";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172358453";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125018;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125018";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:116:"I&#039;m still not sure whether or not she knows I&#039;m the same person. I&#039;d be willing to bet that she does.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235898";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172359727";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125019;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125019";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:23:"Maydays a clever thing.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417235925";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172359156";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125020;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125020";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:195:"She is. And she&#039;s not actually as intimidating as a lot of people seem to think she is. I mean, she won&#039;t take anybody&#039;s BS, but other than that she&#039;s actually quite friendly.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417236002";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172360771";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125023;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125023";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:109:"She takes mine. But I am BS, entirely. You must have seen some of the times I was harassing/playing with her.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417236066";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172360564";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125025;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125025";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10647";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Vaati";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1191";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:4:"text";s:150:"I have seen. Which is part of why I think she&#039;s so great; she &lt;i&gt;knows&lt;/i&gt; when someone&#039;s trolling and just kind of plays along.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417236168";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#b6a5d1";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172362428";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#dbd9e0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1125026;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1125026";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10663";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Dark_Presence";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"719";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Vaati";s:4:"text";s:214:"It&#039;s great fun. She hates being forced into things too, hence why I &#039;offer&#039; hugs and other such things, or she just dodges or parries. She is great, and for what Filly stands for, she&#039;s perfect.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1417236251";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#633600";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14172362414";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#613400";s:16:"chat_log_typ